.:: Puzzle 7x7-Level-3-7::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, whist, poker, chess, snooker, mah-jongg
The people have 7 different jobs:  manager, scientist, dancer, writer, electrician, freelancer, doctor
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: october, april, june, march, september, august, november
